articles.title: Huge asteroid the size of Big Ben will get closer to Earth than the MOON on Saturday - Daily Mail
articles.description: The asteroid, dubbed '2023 DZ2', is estimated to be up to 305 feet in diameter. NASA scientists say that an object of this size passing so close to Earth  happens 'only about once per decade'.
